.TH MKSTRING 3S "Sphinx Informix Tools"
.SH NAME
mkstring \(em make string of replicated character
.SH SYNOPSIS
LET uline = mkstring('-', nchars)
.SH DESCRIPTION
This function returns a string of \fInchars\fP replications of the character
provided as the first argument.
Typically, this is used to create underlines for use in reports.
